This will allow enough for others to have at least enough to create 1 full download again...otherwise the torrent is dead.  You completed the download by others keeping their torrents active, now you need to share otherwise the torrent dies and others get stuck with a partial torrent with no way to finish.  If you have this torrent, please seed for a while so others can finish
